cu.explanation_en: Setting the active gNB name to an invalid string will cause configuration parsing failure and prevent the CU from starting properly.

du.explanation_en: Setting the active gNB name to an invalid string will cause configuration parsing failure and prevent the DU from starting properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將活躍 gNB 名稱設定為無效字串會導致配置解析失敗，並阻止 DU 正確啟動。
